This demo runs on either the STM32VL or STM32L discovery boards.
In both cases, there is a (TX only) debug usart on PA2 (115200@8n1)

** STM32VL discovery board (STM32F100)

MRF24J40MA module wired as follows.

SPI on SPI1 (PA5,6,7)
ChipSelect on PA4
Reset on PC1
Interrupt on PC0

** STM32L discovery board (STM32L15x)

MRF24J40MA module wired as follows.

SPI on SPI2 (PB13,14,15)
ChipSelect on PB12
Reset not connected (tied high)
Interrupt on PB2
